name: Standard Monogram (1)
description:
Standard monograms are personalized with your names, event date and colors only. (NO font changes, removing the date, layout changes, etc. are included.) 

Standard designs are delivered with 5 business days once payment is received.

PLEASE INCLUDE THE FOLLOWING AS A NOTE ON YOUR PAYPAL PAYMENT: Names, wedding date, wedding colors, and the number of the standard monogram you are ordering.

Monograms are for personal use only.

name: Custom Monogram
description:
For a custom monogram, 5 digital samples are sent once a custom monogram order has been placed. Custom monogram drafts are delivered within 15 business days once payment is received.

Changes will be made to the chosen design until the customer gives final approval. Once final approval is given, any changes will result in additional fees.

Monograms are for personal use only.
